## ====================================================================
## rag_test — gitignore
##
## We do NOT vendor the 4 external RAG systems (HippoRAG2 / RAPTOR /
## ComoRAG / A-RAG) — they live as siblings of this repo. See
## EXTERNAL_REPOS.md for the expected layout.
## ====================================================================

# -- External system repos (sibling — never inside) --
ComoRAG/
HippoRAG/
raptor/
arag/
hipporag2/*

# -- Local config / secrets --
.env
config/paths.yaml         # ← per-machine override; .example is tracked
.idea/*

# -- Generated outputs (kept out of git; regenerated by run_all.sh) --
outputs/
nohup_out/
*.log
clear_outputs_and_logs.sh

# Per-experiment results — KEEP the canonical metrics JSON checked in
# (so the headline table is reproducible without re-running anything),
# but ignore the bulky per-query predictions + smoke-test artifacts.
experiments/exp-*/results/predictions.jsonl
experiments/exp-*/results/*.predictions.json
experiments/exp-*/results/*_smoke*

# -- Auto-generated comparison artifact --
reports/RAG_COMPARISON_NARRATIVEQA_table.md

# -- Python --
*.pyc
*.pyd
*.pyo
__pycache__/

# -- Test / scratch --
test_example.ipynb
test_example.py
